- RECURSION IS EVERYWHERE

- Recursion is used in all data structures
  * array
  * string
  * tree
  * graph
  * stack
  * heap
 
 - Algorithms based on recurion
  * dynamic programming
  * backtracking
  * divide and conquer
  
- Recursion problems
  * printing numbers from 1 to n and n to 1
  * sorting an array
  * sorting a stack
  * delete middle element of a stack
  * remove duplicates from a string
  * count the number of occurrences in a string
  * subsets
  * permutations
  * josephus problem
  
- extended input-output method
  * binary string problems
  * generating balanced paranthesis
